<div class="panel">
  <div class="panel-head">
    <h3 class="panel-title">Order Contact Info</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="panel-body">
    <p>
      When your restaurant receives a new order through Goodybag, 
      you will be automatically notified via text, email, and phone
      call. If the order isn't accepted within an hour, we will try
      contacting you directly. Please note that the more contacts you
      enter, the better chances we have of getting in touch.
    </p>
    <div class="contact-group">
      <h4 class="panel-subtitle">MAIN CONTACT</h4>
      <hr>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label class="label-left">Contact Name</label>
        <input type="text" class="form-control" name="contact_name">
        <p class="panel-info">When you receive an order, this person will be notified</p>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label class="label-left">Contact Number</label>
        <input type="text" class="form-control" name="contact_number">
        <p class="panel-info">When you receive an order, this number will be called and
          texted (if it's a cellular number).</p>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label class="label-left">Contact Email</label>
        <input type="text" class="form-control" name="contact_email">
        <p class="panel-info">When you receive an order, we will send an email here.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-list"></div>
    <div>
      <button class="btn btn-default btn-add-contact">+ Add Contact</button>
      <p class="panel-info">You can add more contacts at any point in the future</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
